Non-Commercial Use (Free Tier)

BrightApps permits individuals to use the Software without charge for personal, educational, or non-commercial research purposes.

“Non-commercial” means use that is not on behalf of a business, organization, or for revenue-generating or operational purposes.

Any use by or on behalf of a company, government entity, or other organization is considered commercial use and requires a paid subscription.

BrightApps may modify or revoke non-commercial use rights at any time.
